pageContext.description: Dimensions: EL 102mm; EWe 44mm; W Body at break 23.2mm; EB fg. 19.5mm,Wt. 252.5 gms,Typology: traces of orig. mediial ridge on bl. faces; 'U' shield ridge; hint of bump - prob. stop on one face, not defineable,Manufacture: cavities in one fg. - pore holes?; v. sl. traces of line of cg. fl;,Condition: central part of e. blunt - poss. just corr. dam; both bl. corners broken - pres in ant - dusty corr. surs. with embedded soil; haft break also corr. sur. with embedded soil; fg. crests prob. old  dam. badly from corr.,Attached Material: yellow fawn soil traces
